eb.archive.org/web/20080613231707/http://www.kcchiefs.com/news/2008/06/11/chiefs_agree_to_terms_with_cb_brandon_carr/ |date=June 13, 2008 }}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" |6\n|170\n|[[Barry Richardson (American football)|Barry Richardson]]\n|[[Offensive tackle]]\n|[[Clemson Tigers football|Clemson]]\n|Three years<ref>[http://kcchiefs.com/news/2008/06/25/chiefs_agree_to_terms_with_t_barry_richardson/ Chiefs agree to terms with T Barry Richardson] ''KCChiefs.com'', June 25, 2008.  {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080626185706/http://kcchiefs.com/news/2008/06/25/chiefs_agree_to_terms_with_t_barry_richardson/ |date=June 26, 2008 }}</ref>\n|-\n|182{{Ref label|Minnesota|a|a}}{{Ref label|Tampa Bay|c|c}}\n|[[Kevin Robinson (gridiron football)|Kevin Robinson]]\n|[[Wide receiver]]\n|[[Utah State University|Utah State]]\n|Three years<ref name=\"Robinson, Johnston\">[http://www.kcchiefs.com/news/2008/07/16/chiefs_agree_to_terms_with_wr_kevin_robinson__de_brian_johnston/ Chiefs agree to terms with WR Kevin Robinson & DE Brian Johnston] ''KCChiefs.com'', July 16, 2008.  {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080719100547/http://www.kcchiefs.com/news/2008/07/16/chiefs_agree_to_terms_with_wr_kevin_robinson__de_brian_johnston/ |date=July 19, 2008 }}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" |7\n|210\n|[[Brian Johnston (American football)|Brian Johnston]]\n|[[Linebacker]]\n|[[Gardner\u2013Webb University|Gardner\u2013Webb]]\n|Three years<ref name=\"Robinson, Johnston\"/>\n|-\n|239{{Ref label|New York|d|d}}\n|[[Michael Merritt (American football)|Michael Merritt]]\n|[[Tight end]]\n|[[UCF Knights football|Central Florida]]\n|Three years<ref>[http://www.kcchiefs.com/news/2008/08/25/chiefs_agree_to_terms_with_te_michael_merritt/ Chiefs agree to terms with TE Michael Merritt]  {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080827201457/http://www.kcchiefs.com/news/2008/08/25/chiefs_agree_to_terms_with_te_michael_merritt/ |date=August 27, 2008 }}</ref>\n|}\n\n'''Notes''':\n:{{note label|Minnesota|a|a}} Obtained [[Minnesota Vikings|Minnesota's]] first round selection (#17), and two third round selections (#73, #82) in exchange for DE [[Jared Allen]]. The teams also swapped sixth round selections (Kansas City moved from #187 to #182).<ref name=\"Allen to Vikes\"/>\n:{{note label|Miami|b|b}} Obtained [[Miami Dolphins|Miami's]] fifth round selection (#136) in exchange for QB [[Trent Green]].<ref name=\"Chiefs secure\"/> The selection was later traded to [[Detroit Lions|Detroit]].<ref name=\"2008 Kansas City Chiefs Draft\"/>\n:{{note label|Tampa Bay|c|c}} Obtained [[Tampa Bay Buccaneers|Tampa Bay's]] sixth round selection (#187) in exchange for RB [[Michael Bennett (running back)|Michael Bennett]].<ref name=\"Chiefs secure\"/> The selection was later swapped with Minnesota.<ref name=\"Allen to Vikes\"/>\n:{{note label|New York|d|d}} Obtained [[New York Giants|New York's]] seventh round selection (#239) in exchange for K [[Lawrence Tynes]].<ref name=\"Chiefs secure\"/>\n:{{note label|Detroit|e|e}} '''(Draft day trade)''' Obtained [[Detroit Lions|Detroit's]] first round selection (#15) and third round selection (#76) in exchange for the Chiefs' first round selection (#17), third round selection (#66) and fifth round selection (#136).<ref name=\"2008 Kansas City Chiefs Draft\">[http://www.kcchiefs.com/news/2008/04/27/2008_kansas_city_chiefs_draft/ 2008 Kansas City Chiefs Draft] ''KCChiefs.com'', April 27, 2008.  {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080430234226/http://www.kcchiefs.com/news/2008/04/27/2008_kansas_city_chiefs_draft/ |date=April 30, 2008 }}</ref>\n\n===Roster===\n{| class=\"toccolours\" style=\"text-align: left;\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"9\" style=\"background:#b20032; color:#f2c800; text-align:center;\"|'''Kansas City Chiefs 2008 final roster'''\n|-\n|  style=\"font-size:95%; vertical-align:top;\"| '''Quarterbacks'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">&nbsp;8</span> [[Quinn Gray]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\"