o terms with S DaJuaN Morgan] ''KCChiefs.com'', July 18, 2008.  {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080721230007/http://www.kcchiefs.com/news/2008/07/18/chiefs_agree_to_terms_with_s_dajuan_morgan/ |date=July 21, 2008 }}</ref>\n|-\n|4\n|105\n|[[Will Franklin (American football)|Will Franklin]]\n|[[Wide receiver]]\n|[[Missouri Tigers football|Missouri]]\n|Four years<ref>[http://kcchiefs.com/news/2008/06/18/chiefs_agree_to_terms_with_wr_will_franklin/ Chiefs agree to terms with WR Will Franklin] ''KCChiefs.com'', June 19, 2008.  {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080619020846/http://kcchiefs.com/news/2008/06/18/chiefs_agree_to_terms_with_wr_will_franklin/ |date=June 19, 2008 }}</ref>\n|-\n|5\n|140{{Ref label|Detroit|e|e}}\n|[[Brandon Carr]]\n|[[Defensive back|Cornerback]]\n|[[Grand Valley State University|Grand Valley State]]\n|Three years<ref>[http://www.kcchiefs.com/news/2008/06/11/chiefs_agree_to_terms_with_cb_brandon_carr/ Chiefs agree to terms with CB Brandon Carr] ''KCChiefs.com'', June 11, 2008.  {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080613231707/http://www.kcchiefs.com/news/2008/06/11/chiefs_agree_to_terms_with_cb_brandon_carr/ |date=June 13, 2008 }}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" |6\n|170\n|[[Barry Richardson (American football)|Barry Richardson]]\n|[[Offensive tackle]]\n|[[Clemson Tigers football|Clemson]]\n|Three years<ref>[http://kcchiefs.com/news/2008/06/25/chiefs_agree_to_terms_with_t_barry_richardson/ Chiefs agree to terms with T Barry Richardson] ''KCChiefs.com'', June 25, 2008.  {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080626185706/http://kcchiefs.com/news/2008/06/25/chiefs_agree_to_terms_with_t_barry_richardson/ |date=June 26, 2008 }}</ref>\n|-\n|182{{Ref label|Minnesota|a|a}}{{Ref label|Tampa Bay|c|c}}\n|[[Kevin Robinson (gridiron football)|Kevin Robinson]]\n|[[Wide receiver]]\n|[[Utah State University|Utah State]]\n|Three years<ref name=\"Robinson, Johnston\">[http://www.kcchiefs.com/news/2008/07/16/chiefs_agree_