in exchange for K [[Lawrence Tynes]].<ref name=\"Chiefs secure\"/>\n:{{note label|Detroit|e|e}} '''(Draft day trade)''' Obtained [[Detroit Lions|Detroit's]] first round selection (#15) and third round selection (#76) in exchange for the Chiefs' first round selection (#17), third round selection (#66) and fifth round selection (#136).<ref name=\"2008 Kansas City Chiefs Draft\">[http://www.kcchiefs.com/news/2008/04/27/2008_kansas_city_chiefs_draft/ 2008 Kansas City Chiefs Draft] ''KCChiefs.com'', April 27, 2008.  {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080430234226/http://www.kcchiefs.com/news/2008/04/27/2008_kansas_city_chiefs_draft/ |date=April 30, 2008 }}</ref>\n\n===Roster===\n{| class=\"toccolours\" style=\"text-align: left;\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"9\" style=\"background:#b20032; color:#f2c800; text-align:center;\"|'''Kansas City Chiefs 2008 final roster'''\n|-\n|  style=\"font-size:95%; vertical-align:top;\"| '''Quarterbacks'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">&nbsp;8</span> [[Quinn Gray]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">&nbsp;4</span> [[Tyler Thigpen]]\n\n'''Running Backs'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">26</span> [[Jackie Battle]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">25</span> ''[[Jamaal Charles]]''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">42</span> ''[[Mike Cox (fullback)|Mike Cox]]'' FB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">27</span> [[Larry Johnson (running back)|Larry Johnson]]\n\n'''Wide Receivers'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">82</span> [[Dwayne Bowe]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">83</span> [[Mark Bradley]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">89</span> [[Devard Darling]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">85</span> ''[[Will Franklin (American football)|Will Franklin]]''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">14</span> ''[[Kevin Robinson (gridiron football)|Kevin Robinson]]'' KR/PR\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">80</span> [