ased as B-sides for the album's singles, in various configurations.\n\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Bitter Sweet Symphony\n| extra_column = Producer\n| title1 = Lord I Guess I'll Never Know\n| note1 = \n| length1 = 4:52\n| writer1 = Ashcroft\n| extra1 = {{flatlist|\n* The Verve\n* Youth }}\n| title2 = Country Song\n| note2 = \n| length2 = 7:50\n| writer2 = The Verve\n| extra2 = {{flatlist|\n* The Verve\n* Chris Potter\n* [[Owen Morris]]<ref>{{cite web|title=The Verve \u2013 Bitter Sweet Symphony HUTDG 82|url=https://www.discogs.com/The-Verve-Bitter-Sweet-Symphony/release/881598|website=[[Discogs]]|accessdate=1 April 2017}}</ref> }}\n}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| headline = The Drugs Don't Work\n| extra_column = Producer\n| title1 = Never Wanna See You Cry\n| note1 = \n| length1 = 4:32\n| writer1 = Ashcroft\n| extra1 = {{flatlist|\n* The Verve\n* Chris Potter <ref name=\"The Drugs Don't Work\">{{cite web|title=The Verve \u2013 The Drugs Don't Work HUT CD88|url=https://www.discogs.com/Verve-The-Drugs-Dont-Work/release/1768360|website=[[Discogs]]|accessdate=1 April 2017}}</ref> }}\n| title2 = MSG\n| note2 = \n| length2 = 7:02\n| writer2 = The Verve\n| extra2 = {{flatlist|\n* The Verve\n* Chris Potter<ref name=\"The Drugs Don't Work\" /> }}\n| title3 = The Longest Day\n| note3 = \n| length3 = 7:23\n| writer3 = The Verve\n| extra3 = {{flatlist|\n* The Verve\n* Chris Potter<ref name=\"The Drugs Don't Work\" /> }}\n}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Lucky Man\n| extra_column = Producer\n| title1 = Three Steps\n| note1 = \n| length1 = 5:03\n| writer1 = The Verve\n| extra1 = {{flatlist|\n* The Verve\n* Chris Potter<ref name=\"Lucky Man\">{{cite web|title= The Verve \u2013 Lucky Man HUTT 92|url=https://www.discogs.com/The-Verve-Lucky-Man/release/1095320|website=[[Discogs]]|accessdate=1 April 2017}}</ref> }}\n| title2 = The Crab\n| note2 = \n| length2 = 5:34\n| writer2 = Ashcroft\n| extra2 = {{flatlist|\n* The Verve\n* Chris Potter\n* [[John Leckie]]<ref name=\"Lucky Man\" /> }}\